ust_post_time","QuestionID":"QID1721185864"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b2ULL6XxhpfseDY","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1721185865","SecondaryAttribute":"On the following page, you will have the opportunity to allocate real money between yourself and...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"Q16","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"On the following page, you will have the opportunity to allocate real money between yourself and...","QuestionText":"On the following page, you will have the opportunity to allocate <strong>real money<\/strong> between yourself and a non-profit organization.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nAfter data collection is complete, we will randomly select 100 participants from this study to receive <strong>a $10 bonus payment<\/strong>.&nbsp;<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIf you are selected, the amount you allocate to yourself will be paid to you as a bonus, and the amount you allocate to the organization will be donated on your behalf.","QuestionText_Unsafe":"On the following page, you will have the opportunity to allocate <strong>real money<\/strong> between yourself and a non-profit organization.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nAfter data collection is complete, we will randomly select 100 participants from this study to receive <strong>a $10 bonus payment<\/strong>.&nbsp;<br \/>\n<br \/>\nIf you are selected, the amount you allocate to yourself will be paid to you as a bonus, and the amount you allocate to the organization will be donated on your behalf.","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"QuestionID":"QID1721185865"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b2ULL6XxhpfseDY","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1721185866","SecondaryAttribute":"The organization you can choose to allocate real money to is the American Meteorological Society...","TertiaryAttr