mate change in the following places?","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"alien_info","QuestionType":"Matrix","Selector":"Likert","SubSelector":"SingleAnswer","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","TextPosition":"inline","ChoiceColumnWidth":25,"WhiteSpace":"OFF","MobileFirst":true,"RepeatHeaders":"middle"},"QuestionDescription":"How often do you see or hear information about climate change in the following places?","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Traditional media (e.g., newspapers, TV, radio)"},"2":{"Display":"Online news (e.g., news websites, podcasts, YouTube)"},"3":{"Display":"Social media (e.g., Facebook, TikTok, Instagram)"},"4":{"Display":"Fiction (e.g., films, series, books, comics)"},"11":{"Display":"Personal conversations (e.g., talking with friends or family, text messages, messaging apps)"},"12":{"Display":"In-person events (e.g., museums, public talks)"}},"ChoiceOrder":[1,2,3,4,"11","12"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"RequestResponse","ForceResponseType":"RequestResponse","Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":13,"NextAnswerId":10,"Answers":{"1":{"Display":"Never"},"2":{"Display":"Rarely"},"3":{"Display":"Occasionally"},"8":{"Display":"Frequently"},"9":{"Display":"Very frequently"}},"AnswerOrder":[1,2,3,"8","9"],"ChoiceDataExportTags":{"1":"alien_info_1","2":"alien_info_2","3":"alien_info_3","4":"alien_info_4","11":"alien_info_11","12":"alien_info_12"},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"How often do you see or hear information about climate change in the following places?","QuestionID":"QID1721186003"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b2ULL6XxhpfseDY","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1721186004","SecondaryAttribute":"Timing","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Timing","DefaultChoices":false,"QuestionType":"Timing","Selector":"PageTimer","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","MinSeconds":"0","MaxSeconds":"0"},"QuestionDescription":"Timing","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Click"},"2":{"Display":"Last Click"},"3":{"Display":"Page Submit"},"4":{"Display":"Click Count"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":72,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"QuestionText_Unsafe":"Timing","DataExportTag":"alien_time","QuestionID":"QID1721186004"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b2ULL6XxhpfseDY","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1721186005","SecondaryAttribute":"Learn more about climate science \u00a0 If you\u2019d like to learn more about climate science and solution","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[],"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"newsletter_stim","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Learn more about climate science \u00a0 If you\u2019d like to learn more about climate science and solution...","QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnload(function () {\n  \/\/ --- Track link click time\n  var link = document.getElementById('openLink');\n  if (link) {\n    link.addEventListener('click', function () {\n      Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('TalkingClimateLinkClickedAt', new Date().toISOString());\n      \/\/ Mark we opened the external site\n      Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('TalkingClimateLinkClicked', '1');\n    });\n  }\n\n  \/\/ --- Estimate time away on external page using visibility changes\n  var hiddenAt = null, totalHiddenMs = 0;\n  document.addEventListener('visibilitychange', function () {\n    if (document.hidden) {\n      hiddenAt = Date.now();\n    } else if (hiddenAt) {\n      totalHiddenMs += (Date.now() - hiddenAt);\n      hiddenAt = null;\n      Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('TalkingClimateExternalVisitSeconds', Math.round(totalHiddenMs \/ 1000));\n    }\n  });\n\n  \/\/ --- Save optional subscription status immediately on change\n  var radios = this.getQuestionContainer().querySelectorAll('input[name=\"subStatus\"]');\n  radios.forEach(function(r) {\n    r.addEventListener('change', function () {\n      Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('TalkingClimateSubscribedStatus', this.value);\n    });\n  });\n});\n\nQualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnPageSubmit(function () {\n  \/\/ Final write of current values (in case user didn\u2019t change after selecting)\n  var selected = this.getQuestionContainer().querySelector('input[name=\"subStatus\"]:checked');\n  Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.setEmbeddedData('TalkingClimateSubscribedStatus', selected ? selected.value : '');\n});","QuestionText":"<h3>Learn more about climate science<\/h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;d like to learn more about climate science and solutions, you can subscribe to the newsletter by climate scientist Katharine Hayhoe.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nHer newsletter &quot;Talking Climate&quot; provides short, accessible updates on climate science and climate solutions for a general audience.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSigning up takes less than a minute. Please select the free subscription option &mdash; there is no need to choose a paid version.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe link below will open the newsletter in a new tab. You can switch back to the current tab and continue the survey right away.<br \/>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:.5rem 0 .75rem 0;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.talkingclimate.ca\/?source=qualtrics&amp;rid=${e:\/\/Field\/ResponseID}\" id=\"openLink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.6rem .9rem; border:1px solid #aaa; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\">Open Talking Climate newsletter (opens in a new tab) <\/a><\/p>\n\n<hr style=\"margin:1rem 0;\" \/>\n<p style=\"margin:.5rem 0;\"><i><b>Note<\/b>: Subscribing to this newsletter is optional. <\/i><\/p>\n\n<div aria-label=\"Subscription status\" id=\"statusGroup\" role=\"radiogroup\">&nbsp;<\/div>","QuestionText_Unsafe":"<h3>Learn more about climate science<\/h3>\n&nbsp;\n\n<p>If you&rsquo;d like to learn more about climate science and solutions, you can subscribe to the newsletter by climate scientist Katharine Hayhoe.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nHer newsletter &quot;Talking Climate&quot; provides short, accessible updates on climate science and climate solutions for a general audience.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nSigning up takes less than a minute. Please select the free subscription option &mdash; there is no need to choose a paid version.<br \/>\n<br \/>\nThe link below will open the newsletter in a new tab. You can switch back to the current tab and continue the survey right away.<br \/>\n&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n<p style=\"margin:.5rem 0 .75rem 0;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.talkingclimate.ca\/?source=qualtrics&amp;rid=${e:\/\/Field\/ResponseID}\" id=\"openLink\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"display:inline-block; padding:.6rem .9rem; border:1px solid #aaa; border-radius:6px; text-decoration:none;\" target=\"_blank\">Open Talking Climate newsletter (opens in a new tab) <\/a><\/p>\n\n<hr style=\"margin:1rem 0;\" \/>\n<p style=\"margin:.5rem 0;\"><i><b>Note<\/b>: Subscribing to this newsletter is optional. <\/i><\/p>\n\n<div aria-label=\"Subscription status\" id=\"statusGroup\" role=\"radiogroup\">&nbsp;<\/div>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"QuestionID":"QID1721186005"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_b2ULL6XxhpfseDY","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1721186006","SecondaryAttribute":"Did you subscribe to the \u201cTalking Climate\u201d newsletter on the previous page?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"ChoiceOrder":[1,2],"Choices":{"1":{"Display":"Yes"},"2":{"Display":"No"}},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataExportTag":"newsletter","DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":3,"QuestionDescription":"Did you subscribe to the \u201cTalking Climate\u201d newsletter on the previous page?","QuestionText":"Did you subscribe to the \u20